item.title: Deltascape home
item.dc:creator: @Randomking17 Randomking17
item.description:
@Randomking17 wrote:

Let’s make this quick.

Open up clickingmost.java and push CTRL+F
Search this:

case 73100: case 4140: case 50235: c.triggerTele(2999+misc.random(3), 3377+misc.random(3), 0); break;
Change the coords of it to whatever you want.

Your very welcome.
As I, Always wanted to know how to do this, and I taught myself.

item.title: Deltascape home
item.dc:creator: @Mrs_Extro_Limited Mrs Extro Limited
item.description:
@Mrs_Extro_Limited wrote:

Okay, well you first need to add a mypos or coords command to your server.

if(command.startsWith("mypos") && playerRights > 0){ sM("AbsX: "+absX+" AbsY: "+absY+""); }

stand in the place you would like to put as your starter home and then type ::mypos
it will give you a message of where you are standing, replace the X and Y with the one in player.java

Hope i helped
